{"tid":372653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump: 金正恩開始尊重美國  北韓: 同日發放轟炸關島宣傳片","createTime":"2017-08-24T12:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T01:16:44.000Z","uid":76115,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d01496be982baa922da2e9f7fc7c2c5906eb8d4f","tid":372653,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2172490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2172490&d=XVmCOPbwgKlZqwi1%2FIL3dCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b110ed90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2172490&h=962e1e75\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2172490</a><br />\n<br />\n川普稱「金正恩開始尊重美國」...北韓同日播出炸關島 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpStnHSO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpStnHSO.jpg&h=18b53ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓昨日發布一部砲轟美國的影片，宣示意味濃厚。（圖片擷取自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕北韓近日因放話砲轟關島，讓朝鮮半島局勢升溫。美國總統川普則在造勢場合上，稱金正恩「開始尊重我們了」，但北韓在同一天，正好釋出一部砲轟美國的宣傳片。<br />\n<br />\n川普在當地時間22日，於美國亞利桑那州鳳凰城舉辦造勢大會，他在過程中提到，近來對金正恩的警告開始奏效，「有人說這樣太強烈，但其實不夠強烈」，聲稱金正恩「開始尊重我們了」、「有些正面的事情可能發生」。<br />\n<br />\n但在同一天，北韓釋出一段砲轟關島的宣傳片，片中充斥著飛彈發射、爆炸的場面，並出現大量美軍片段，以及美國副總統彭斯、國防部長馬提斯、國務卿提勒森等人被火焰燃燒，川普則正對著一片廢墟與墳墓，最後則是北韓閱兵的畫面，宣示意味濃厚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTs_llzhyik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTs_llzhyik&d=XVmCOPbwgKlZqwi1%2FIL3dCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a570b2e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTs_llzhyik</a>"},{"pid":"2b7a3feda1fce3d928c1086853f6a01001bf0226","tid":372653,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:51:07.000Z","msg":"Trump話maybe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59beb1cb027136095b928b8f1bf6070a10251ba","tid":372653,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兜巴星"},{"pid":"5f87b4605922d8a12964450e4af9f0268c62d313","tid":372653,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"大巴大巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026e85e9407516c0872c71135e7df0f7ebaacb18","tid":372653,"uid":76115,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兜巴星</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://replygif.net/i/1196.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Freplygif.net%2Fi%2F1196.gif&h=83716c60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12d4200885d63e3bebca7c0b17e4c070d1e9bbfa","tid":372653,"uid":13468,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/03/30/3912_20160330123347_56fb572be6d62.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F03%2F30%2F3912_20160330123347_56fb572be6d62.gif&h=c92f947a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa3ea2f049135614158863f5866572f9ad53ed2e","tid":372653,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23ceca5dd1a1716a7db5a7a9642ceb9a869d8c8a","tid":372653,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"打未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a422a809ad2d6d7b319cf78fd80d22075eff17c9","tid":372653,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:34:36.000Z","msg":"之前 Trump 講過, 如果金正恩停止再射導彈, 可以安排同金正恩見面<br />\n但金正恩 唔理, 照射<br />\n<br />\n如果金正恩 真係去美國同Trump見面, 會唔會變左 鴻門宴"},{"pid":"52536965a315518836115876328a2c5e6bcadeb5","tid":372653,"uid":65128,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e6bf42cae66a2c1ea9afdeeacc239af9faad1a4","tid":372653,"uid":87780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"侵真係幾冇用下"},{"pid":"6bb34604936d011cde7540c9e5d4398612af3263","tid":372653,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9dc523eacc6f80f5b5dda1d409641f36069c3f1","tid":372653,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:38:17.000Z","msg":"兩條友喺道打嘴炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c363ffd9c1940597f8032f3e9ac0e0e3881eeb","tid":372653,"uid":9542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"兩邊都精神勝利左大家，互相各自飛機，用黎轉移國內視線，但明明大家咩實質野都無做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c6f26023450ca9ddfabcd6a171ad3be671e809","tid":372653,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩邊都精神勝利左大家，互相各自打飛機，用黎轉移國內視線，但明明大家咩實質野都無做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"84d42159294c12c29855b73f5e5ea6fe6501bb5e","tid":372653,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/03/30/3912_20160330123347_56fb572be6d62.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F03%2F30%2F3912_20160330123